OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the evening with late sunny spells.
OL,7,FRemaining dry overnight with clear
OL,8,Fspells. Light winds and turning
OL,9,Fchilly, especially in rural spots.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FDry at first on Monday with
OL,12,Fsome sunshine. Turning cloudier during
OL,13,Fthe afternoon and breezier as a spell
OL,14,Fof rain, mainly across Cumbria arrives
OL,15,Flater in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
